-bill?source=3Dem160701"><strong>Can you write to your senators today =
and ask them to oppose the GMO bill? You can click here and we'll direct =
you to write your senators immediately.</strong></a></p>
<p align=3D"center">
	<a =
href=3D"https://go.berniesanders.com/page/speakout/stop-the-gmo-labeling-=
