States should be able to decide for themselves &ndash; without =
multinational corporations getting involved &ndash; if they want their =
food to be labeled.</strong></a></p>
<p style=3D"font-size:17px; line-height:140%;">
	Thanks for standing up to Monsanto on this issue.</p>
